<br>
Something to let me keep notes, in a brief and handy form, about the folks on my Buddy List.<br>
<br>
Especially after a day like yesterday, there is no way my poor middle-aged brain is going to remember all the people I teamed with.<br>
<br>
I keep my list pretty trimmed; once a day or so I go through the &quot;?&quot; section, move the few I want to keep into the &quot;Approved&quot; section, and use the &quot;!cc rembuddy ?&quot; command to purge the rest.<br>
<br>
But still...<br>
<br>
How am I supposed to remember who the hell &quot;Xiggernoogiepop&quot; or &quot;D3thch1ld3&quot; was?<br>
<br>
